snippet.title: Tummy Bonbons: The Sweet Monster 🍭 Free Game Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Eat candy. Get spookier. Scare children into giving you their candy. Eat it. Choose new bellies. Then eat more candy, as much as you can!

Get Tummy Bonbons for free!
🍭 On Itch: https://punkcake.itch.io/tummy-bonbons
🍬 On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3297190/Tummy_Bonbons_The_Sweet_Monster
💖 Subscribe to our Patreon for monthly game releases: https://patreon.com/punkcake
💬 Join our community on Discord: https://discord.gg/TkdktuKBgp

Tummy Bonbons is the first Punkcake game from our newest recruit, Eris! Please show her lots of love by giving the game positive reviews on Steam!
